The use of deep learning techniques such as deep sets encoding and modular RL also suggests that it could belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper mentions object detection, which is a common topic in the cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-category. Finally, the use of RL for control suggests that it could also belong to the cs.SY (Systems and Control) sub-category.
